</ul>', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'jalan Arcana, kelod Kangin, desa Bondalem, kecamatan Tejakula', -8.1103861501576, 115.31915187836, '[]', NULL, 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2023-11-09 20:51:32', 1);
