Located on the upper floor of the 11-bedroom beachfront compound with an astonishing sea view.
Only 2 rooms of this kind.
The most popular choice for honeymooners, lovers, for those who want to make amazing selfies in flower bath. Upon request your bathtub can be refilled with fresh flowers. Breathtaking view of Bali Sea and sunrises. Amenities: electric kettle, shower, bathtub on veranda, safety deposit box, TV, Air conditioning, balcony with front sea view, bathrobe and slippers, hairdryer, free toiletries, dressing room, drying rack for clothes.
Bondalem Beach Club is located in a traditional Bali village. Right on the seafront with colorful coral reef alongside a shoreline. The best of Bali waterfalls located nearby.', 'Bali', 'indonesia', 'jalan Arcana, kelod Kangin, desa Bondalem, kecamatan Tejakula', -8.1104073932117, 115.31915187836, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Bar / Restaurant", "Parking on Premises", "Gym", "Pool", "TV", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2023-11-10 15:59:03', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('2-bedroom Garden Villa', '2-bedroom-garden-villa', 'For those who want more tranquility and authentic Bali experience we are offering accommodation in a 2-bedroom villa located only 80 steps from Bondalem Beach Club main territory, 100 steps from the beach, not on the beach, but surrounded with a lush fruit garden - papaya, mango, rambutan - for a period of your stay it will be exclusively your garden.
Villa consists of 2 bedrooms equipped with king-size beds, air conditions, showers. Fully equipped kitchen. Rooms have no TV.
Guests use all facilities provided by Bondalem Beach Club while enjoying more privacy and tranquility.
Amenities: electric kettle, shower, Air conditioning, hairdryer, bathrobe and slippers, refrigerator, ironing facilities, seating area, free toiletries, washing machine, private bathroom, kitchen/kitchenware/dining area, private entrance, mosquito net, garden view, terrace, drying rack for clothes.', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'jalan Arcana, kelod Kangin, desa Bondalem, kecamatan Tejakula', -8.1115332734709, 115.31850814819, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Bar / Restaurant", "Hair Dryer", "Parking on Premises", "Gym", "Kitchen", "Pool", "Free Wi-Fi"]', NULL, 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2023-11-10 17:12:13', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('M LILOAN PENSION HOUSE/Deluxe Double Room', 'm-liloan-pension-house-deluxe-double-room-3', 'M LILOAN PENSION HOUSE is located in Tayud, Liloan 8 miles from SM City Cebu and 8.4 miles from Ayala Center Cebu. With a bar, the 3-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. Free private parking is available and the hotel also has car rental for guests who want to explore the surrounding area.

The rooms come with a flat-screen TV with cable channels, an electric tea pot, a bidet, free toiletries and a desk. At the hotel rooms have bed linen and towels.

A continental breakfast is available each morning at M LILOAN PENSION HOUSE.

Speaking English and Filipino at the 24-hour front desk, staff are ready to help around the clock.

Fuente Osmena Circle is 9.3 miles from the accommodation, while Magellan''s Cross is 10 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Mactan-Cebu International Airport, 7.5 miles from M LILOAN PENSION HOUSE.', 'Liloan', 'Philippines', 'Purok Mahogany 2, Tayud, Liloan, Philippines, 6002 Catarman, Philippines', 10.373496524945, 123.98536920547, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Bar / Restaurant", "Parking on Premises", "TV", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2023-11-10 23:28:54', 1);
