INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Wedgewood Residences Mont Kiara / 2 Bedroom Suite', 'wedgewood-residences-mont-kiara-2-bedroom-suite', 'Featuring an outdoor pool and a kids'' playground, Wedgewood Residences offers spacious and modern apartments. It is located 400 metres from SohoKL shopping centre. Free WiFi is accessible in all areas and free private parking is provided for guests who drive.

Each air-conditioned apartment includes a living area with a cable TV and a well-equipped kitchen. Some units have a dining area. The en suite bathroom is fitted with a bath, a shower and a hairdryer.

Guests enjoy daily buffet breakfast, served at the Garden Room. Other dining options are located within a 5-minute walk from the property.

Guests can relax by the pool or exercise in the fitness centre, while kids can play in the playground. The friendly staff at the 24/7 reception can help you with airport transfers and bicycle hires at an additional charge.

MATRADE Exhibition and Convention Centre is 1.6 km from Wedgewood Residences, while National Palace is 6.5 km from the property. The nearest airport is Sultan Abdul Aziz Shah Airport, 27 km drive away.

Additional services as below :
· Airport pick up / drop (additional cost and types of vehicle)
· Private shuttle to other destination and tour (additional cost)
· Extra bed (additional cost)
· Breakfast (additional cost)
· Meeting room (additional cost)
· AV charger for electric vehicle (additional cost)

Rates quoted include the following features and privileges
 Fully furnished suites with unsuited bathroom with bathtub &amp; shower.
 Free High-Speed WI-FI.
 Bedroom with INDIVIDUAL bathroom.
 Bedroom 1 set-up with a Queen-sized bed complete with private bathroom.
 Bedroom 2 set-up with a Twin single sized bed complete with private
bathroom.
 In-room digital safe, hair dryer, iron and ironing board.
 Smart TV with Netflix in living area and LED TV in bedroom with
centralized cable channels.
 Suite with kitchenette (Fully Equipped Kitchen) with Coffee and Tea making
facilities.
 Daily cleaning or weekly cleaning.
 Free washer and dryer.
 Free parking.

Wedgewood Residences Facilities:
 24 hours reception, concierge and Shuttle Services.
 Swimming pool &amp; Table Tennis.
 24 Gym, 24 CCTV and Security.
Complimentary shuttle service (return) to International School as below :
・LFKL / France International School (primary &amp; secondary)
