Nearby to airport and tourist places such F1 Sepang International Circuit, Cyberjaya Lake Garden, Nilai 3 Wholesale Mall, Putrajaya City, etc.
Very convenient as groceries shop, self-laundry, KIP MALL, restaurants are nearby', 'Kuala Lumpur', 'malaysia', 'no1, lot 5695, jalan7, kampung, baru lanjut, Sepang, selangor', 2.7923796, 101.7086356, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Hair Dryer", "Parking on Premises", "Kitchen", "TV", "Free Wi-Fi"]', NULL, 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2024-04-18 15:22:39', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('GISY Lake House / Bunk Bed in Mixed Dormitory Room', 'gisy-lake-hostel-double-room-with-private-bathroom', 'GISY Lake Hostel has a garden, shared lounge, a terrace and restaurant in Hanoi. 5.6 miles from Thanh Chuong Palace and 24 miles from Vietnam Museum of Ethnology, the property has a private beach area that allows swimming in the lake, as well as a bar. The property is non-smoking in the rooms but allows smoking in the garden and is located 27 miles from West Lake.

At the hostel rooms come with bed linen and towels.

An à la carte breakfast is available each morning at GISY Lake Hostel.

You can play table tennis at the accommodation.

Quan Thanh Temple is 28 miles from GISY Lake Hostel, while Ho Chi Minh Mausoleum is 28 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Noi Bai International Airport, 11 miles from the hostel.', 'Hanoi', 'vietnam', 'Đập hồ Đồng Đò, Minh Tân, Sóc Sơn, Hà Nội 12215 Vietnam', 21.314663793083, 105.77108860016, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Bar / Restaurant", "Parking on Premises", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "Wheelchair Accessible", "Free Wi-Fi"]', NULL, 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2024-06-10 08:12:08', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Double Deluxe Room / The Moon Boutique Hotel', 'double-deluxe-room-with-disability-access-the-moon-boutique-hotel', 'The Moon Boutique Hotel is ideally set in Sofia, and has a shared lounge, free WiFi and a bar. This 3-star hotel offers luggage storage space. The property is non-smoking throughout and is located a 11-minute walk from NDK.

At the hotel, the rooms include a desk, a flat-screen TV, a private bathroom, bed linen and towels. All rooms will provide guests with a closet and an electric tea pot.

The Moon Boutique Hotel offers a continental or vegan breakfast.

Popular points of interest near the accommodation include Sofia University St. Kliment Ohridski, Vasil Levski Stadium Station and Ivan Vazov Theater. The nearest airport is Sofia Airport, 3.7 miles from The Moon Boutique Hotel.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.1 for a two-person trip.', 'sofia', 'bulgaria', 'Sofia Center, bul.', 42.6883975, 23.327212, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Hair Dryer", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "TV", "Wheelchair Accessible", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'Cancellation within 48 hours of arrival is not accepted.', '2024-08-12 20:20:23', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Standard Double room / Bricks Hotel', 'standard-double-room-bricks-hotel-2', 'Embarking on a journey with Hotel Bricks, with an exploration of affordable luxury and superior services. The hotel prides itself on offering a memorable experience From the moment you check in, you''ll find that every detail has been carefully considered to ensure your comfort and satisfaction.

The lobby welcomes you with a modern aesthetic, blending style and functionality. The friendly and efficient staff, trained to provide top-notch service, ensures a smooth check-in process.

The hotel''s commitment to superior service extends to its dining options. The Breakfast offers a diverse menu, featuring flavorful dishes crafted from fresh, locally sourced ingredients.

One of the first highlights is Our location - within walking distance from Freedom Square (1.3 KM), Opera and Ballet Theater of Tbilisi (2 KM), Holy Trinity Cathedral of Tbilisi (1.50 KM), Metekhi church ( 600 Feet), Shardeni Street (200 Feet), Bridge of Peace (400 Feet), aerial Tramwai (200 Feet), Narikala Fortress ( 200Feet )

One of the highlights of your stay is the rooftop terrace, a space where luxury meets affordability. Take advantage of this scenic retreat to unwind after a day of exploration. Whether it''s basking in the sun, enjoying a cup of complimentary coffee, or stargazing in the evening, the terrace becomes your private oasis above the city.

Hotel Bricks understands the importance of connectivity, Complimentary Wi-Fi ensures that you can stay connected with loved ones or catch up on work while enjoying the comfort of your room or the communal spaces.

In addition to providing a comfortable stay, Hotel Bricks has private parking for the guests, air-conditioned rooms with a desk, a kettle, a fridge, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a bidet. At Bricks Hotel every room is equipped with bed linen, towels and hygiene products.

often surprises guests with little touches that elevate the overall experience. Whether it''s a welcome treat, personalized recommendations for local attractions, or the assistance of a dedicated concierge, the hotel goes the extra mile to make your journey special.

Embark on your adventure with Hotel Bricks and Experience the blend of affordability and superior services that redefine what it means to enjoy a journey within your means.', 'Tbilisi', 'Georgia', '17 Wine Rise, Tbilisi 0103 Georgia', 41.692060264633, 44.813677668571, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Hair Dryer", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "TV", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2024-08-13 22:23:43', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Standard Room A Block – King Size Bed / Khedi Hotel, Tbilisi', 'standard-room-a-block-king-size-bed-khedi-hotel-by-ginza-project', 'Khedi Hotel
24 Ketevan Tsamebuli Avenue, 0103 Tbilisi City, Georgia

Set in Tbilisi City, 2.2 km from Freedom Square, Khedi Hotel by offers accommodation with a fitness centre, free private parking, a garden and a terrace. 2.5 km from
Rustaveli Theatre and 2.7 km from Tbilisi Opera and Ballet Theatre, the property features a restaurant and a bar.

The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.

The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, a coffee machine, a fridge, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private
bathroom with a bidet.

The rooms are equipped with a kettle, while some rooms also feature a balcony and others also feature city views.

All guest rooms feature a wardrobe. An à la carte,
American or vegetarian breakfast is available every morning at the property.

Popular points of interest near Khedi Hotel by Ginza Project include Presidential Palace, Metekhi Church and Saint George’s Armenian Cathedral.

The nearest airport is Tbilisi International Airport, 12 km from the accommodation.

<span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>The Morning Plan is not available for same-day reservations.</strong></span>
<span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Bookings must be made by 6:00 PM on the previous day</strong></span>', 'Tbilisi', 'Georgia', '24 Ketevan Tsamebuli Avenue, 0103 Tbilisi, Georgia', 41.689700820593, 44.820179343224, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Bar / Restaurant", "Hair Dryer", "Elevator in Building", "Parking on Premises", "Gym", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "TV", "Wheelchair Accessible", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'The following cancellation policy is set forth by this website and applies at the time of reservation. If\r\nyou cancel on the day of your reservation, 100% of the usage fee will be charged as a cancellation\r\nfee. If you cancel up to the day before your reservation, no cancellation fee will be charged. Please\r\nnote that some facilities may not follow this website''s cancellation policy and may apply their own\r\ncancellation policy. Please be sure to check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of\r\nthe facility you plan to use.', '2024-08-14 16:08:34', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Regency Sealine Camp / Patio Room', 'regency-sealine-camp-patio-room', 'Regency Sealine Camp provides beachfront accommodations in Mesaieed. With a shared lounge, the 5-star luxury tent has air-conditioned rooms with free Wifi, each with a private bathroom. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk and parking on-site.

At the luxury tent, each unit is equipped with a wardrobe.

Buffet and à la carte breakfast options with fresh pastries, pancakes, and fruit are available daily at the luxury tent. Guests can eat at the on-site family-friendly restaurant, which is open for dinner.

For guests with children, Regency Sealine Camp offers outdoor play equipment. The luxury tent also offers outdoor fireplace and a picnic area for a day outdoors.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 8.6 for a two-person trip.', 'Mesaieed', 'qatar', 'InLand Sea Off Rd, Qatar', 24.772707519428, 51.480560302734, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Hair Dryer", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "TV", "Wheelchair Accessible", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel you will be charged 100% of the booking.', '2024-08-16 17:46:36', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Executive King Room', 'executive-king-room-grand-regency-doha-trademark-collection-by-wyndham-2', 'Enjoying a central location in Doha, Decorated with soft carpets and large beds, rooms at Grand Regency Hotel-Doha are equipped with satellite TV channels and tea/coffee makers. Private bathrooms come with courtesy bathrobes and slippers.

Guests can enjoy world-class cuisine in one of the hotel’s establishments, International breakfast, lunch or dinner at Grand Gourmet. The on-site Al Kut Lounge serves European-inspired pastries and coffee brews. No alcoholic drinks are available.

Staff at the 24-hour reception can help plan visits and excursions to the iconic Museum of Islamic Arts or Al Koot Fort, both within a 10-minute drive from the Grand Regency Hotel. Free private parking is available on site.', 'Doha', 'qatar', 'Al Sadd Area, 22606 Doha, Qata', 25.291402863874, 51.497039794922, '["Air Conditioner (Cooling)", "Bar / Restaurant", "Hair Dryer", "Elevator in Building", "Parking on Premises", "Gym", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "Pool", "Projector(s)", "TV", "Wheelchair Accessible", "Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Hotel', 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2024-08-25 22:17:11', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Eagle Town Standard Apartment', 'eagle-town-serviced-apartment-deluxe-double-room-with-balcony', 'You''re eligible for a Genius discount at Eagle Town Serviced Apartment. To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.

Eagle Town Serviced Apartment- Free Pick up from Airport offers accommodations in Ulaanbaatar, 8.6 miles from Ulaanbaatar Opera House and 8.9 miles from National Museum of Mongolian History. Free Wifi is available throughout the property and private parking is available on site. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk and an elevator for guests.

Each room has a private bathroom, while some rooms include a fully equipped kitchen with a microwave. In some units there''s a dressing room for guests to change in.

A mini-market is available at the apartment.

A children''s playground is also available at the apartment, while guests can also relax in the garden.

Mongolia National Park is 9 miles from Eagle Town Serviced Apartment- Free Pick up from Airport, while Sukhbaatar Square is 9.1 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Buyant-Ukhaa International Airport, 0.6 miles from the accommodation.', 'Ulaanbaatar', 'Mongolia', 'Khan Uul district, 21st khoroo, Archive road street, Eagle town, Ulaanbaatar Mongolia, Ulaanbaatar', 47.852608263106, 106.78197026253, '["Bar / Restaurant", "Hair Dryer", "Air Conditioner (Heating)", "Kitchen", "TV", "Free Wi-Fi"]', NULL, 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel on the day of use, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge. If you cancel by the day before the date of use, no cancellation fee will be incurred. Please note that some facilities may not follow the cancellation policy of our site, but instead apply their own unique cancellation policy. Always check the cancellation policy listed on the information page of the facility you plan to use.', '2024-08-28 20:28:36', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Eco-friendly Why Me Tbilisi / Bed in 8-Bed Mixed Dormitory Room', 'why-me-tbilisi-bed-in-8-bed-mixed-dormitory-room', 'This dorm has 4 bunkbeds and can be booked as a private room for large groups. Next to this room is the common bathroom with two showers, two toilets and two sinks.', 'Tbilisi', 'Georgia', 'Zurab Abuladze Str. 5 ap. 2 0163 Tbilisi, Georgia', 41.690508008556, 44.872096180916, '["Hair Dryer", "Kitchen", "Scanner / Printer", "TV", "Free Wi-Fi"]', NULL, 'The cancellation policy outlined below is established by our website and is applied at the time of your reservation. If you cancel within 3 days before arrival, you will be charged 100% of the fee as a cancellation charge.', '2024-08-29 16:17:05', 1);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Meeting Room for 15 at Zero-Ten Park - Makati', 'zero-ten-park-manila', 'Our meeting rooms are designed to provide a professional, comfortable, and fully equipped environment for your team discussions, client presentations, and virtual conferences. Each room includes high-speed internet, HD display or projector, whiteboard, coffee, tea, and water for a seamless meeting experience.', 'Manila', 'philippines', '11F, Frabelle Business Center, 111 Rada, Legazpi Village, Makati City, 1229 Metro Manila', 14.5557052, 121.0179106, '["Free Wi-Fi"]', 'Private Room', 'The following cancellation policy is set forth on our website and applies at the time of reservation.\nCancellation on the day of use will incur a cancellation fee of 100% of the usage fee.\nCancellation up to 24 hours prior to the start of use will not incur a cancellation fee.', '2026-02-09 17:49:44', 1);
