INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Sanur Beach &amp; Village Cycling Tour', 'sanur-beach-village-cycling-tour', 'DESCRIPTION
Escape the traffic and discover the soul of Bali’s oldest resort area on two wheels. This 3-hour guided journey takes you along Sanur’s famous 7km paved beachfront boardwalk—the only path of its kind on the island. You will transition from the refreshing sea breeze of the coast into the heart of traditional Balinese "Banjar" (villages), passing ancient temples and vibrant local markets. This is a low-impact, high-reward experience designed for those who want to see the authentic, "slow" side of Bali life at a leisurely pace.

HIGHLIGHTS

Safe Seaside Cycling: Enjoy a flat, car-free ride along the stunning Sanur coastline.

Authentic Village Life: Weave through quiet backstreets to see traditional Balinese architecture and temples.

Heritage Fishing Spots: Stop at the local boat landings to see the iconic, colorful "Jukung" outrigger boats.

Family-Friendly Terrain: Completely flat route, making it perfect for all fitness levels and ages.

Hidden Sanur: Discover the secret spots that most tourists miss when traveling by car.

INCLUDE

Private Hotel Pickup &amp; Drop-off: Air-conditioned transport from your accommodation.

Bicycle Rental: Well-maintained, comfortable cruiser or mountain bike.

Expert Local Guide: Professional lead to guide the route and share cultural history.

Refreshments: Bottled mineral water throughout the tour.

NOT INCLUDE

Meals: Lunch or heavy snacks (available for purchase at local cafes along the route).

Personal Expenses: Souvenirs or additional drinks during stops.

Gratuities: Tips for your cycling guide and driver.

NOTE

Best Start Time: We recommend an 08:00 AM or 08:30 AM start to enjoy the cooler morning air and the best coastal light.

What to Wear: Comfortable light clothing and closed-toe shoes (sneakers are best). Don''t forget sunglasses and sunscreen.

Fitness Level: This is a "Leisure" tour. The terrain is 100% flat with no hills, suitable for anyone who can comfortably ride a bike.

Photo Opportunities: Your guide is happy to stop at any time to help you take photos of the temples or the ocean.', 'Bali', 'indonesia', 'Jalan Hang Tuah 27, Sanur, Denpasar Selatan', -8.6740896, 115.2602126, '[]', 'Hotel', 'Cancellation on the day of use will incur a cancellation fee of 100% of the usage fee. Cancellation up to 24 hours prior to the start of use will not incur a cancellation fee and fully refunded', '2026-02-25 08:54:38', 1);
