INSERT OR IGNORE INTO hotels (name, slug, description, city, country, address, latitude, longitude, amenities, property_type, cancellation_policy, created_at, is_active) VALUES ('Nusa Dua Snorkeling &amp; Banana Boat Adventure', 'nusa-dua-snorkeling-banana-boat-adventure-copy', 'DESCRIPTION
Experience the best of Bali’s famous water sports in one action-packed session. Start by exploring the quiet side of the ocean with a snorkeling trip to Nusa Dua’s tropical reefs, where you can swim alongside schools of colorful fish. Then, shift gears for a high-speed thrill on the Banana Boat. Towed by a powerful speedboat, you’ll bounce across the waves for an exhilarating ride that is guaranteed to bring out the laughs. It is the perfect half-day "splash" for those who want adventure and nature in one go.

HIGHLIGHTS
Tropical Snorkeling: Discover the underwater beauty of Nusa Dua’s calm, coral-filled lagoons.
Banana Boat Thrill: Group-friendly excitement as you glide and bounce over the ocean surface.
Safe for Beginners: All activities take place in protected waters with professional instructors and life jackets.
Fast-Paced Action: Complete two iconic Bali water sports in a single, efficient 1 to 2-hour session.
Prime Location: Enjoy the premium facilities and clear waters of the Tanjung Benoa/Nusa Dua coast.

INCLUDE
Private Hotel Pickup &amp; Drop-off: Door-to-door service in a private, air-conditioned vehicle.
Equipment Rental: Snorkel, mask, fins, and life jackets for both activities.
Banana Boat Session: One full circuit on a professional inflatable banana boat.
Boat Transfer: Motorized boat to take you to the best snorkeling spots.
Professional Instructor: Safety briefing and on-water guidance for all activities.
Insurance: Standard water sports insurance coverage.

NOT INCLUDE
Personal Documentation: Professional photos or GoPro videos (available for purchase).
Towels: Please bring your own towel or one from your hotel.


NOTE
Tide &amp; Weather: These activities are best enjoyed during mid-to-high tide. We will coordinate your pickup time for the best water conditions.
Age Limit: Suitable for children (usually age 6+) and adults.
What to Wear: Swimwear and a high-SPF sunscreen are essential. A change of clothes is recommended for after the tour.
Safety First: Life jackets are mandatory for both the snorkeling and the banana boat sessions.', 'Bali', 'indonesia', 'Jl. Pratama No.105, Benoa', -8.771518, 115.2222017, '[]', 'Hotel', 'Cancellation on the day of use will incur a cancellation fee of 100% of the usage fee. Cancellation up to 24 hours prior to the start of use will not incur a cancellation fee and fully refunded', '2026-02-25 12:58:48', 1);
